Description_lang: Serendipity reduces the cooldown of your Holy Words by up to an additional ${$m1/1}.1 sec.

description_blz.en_US: Serendipity reduces the cooldown of your Holy Words by up to an additional 1.0 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Serendipia reduce hasta 1.0 s más el tiempo de reutilización de tus Palabras sagradas.

description_blz.de_DE: 'Glücksfall' verringert die Abklingzeit Eurer Segensworte um bis zu 1,0 Sek. zusätzlich.
